{
  "stem": "16503.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as far as I know, maybe we might have lit up the Hanukkah candles because again, we are going to the pretty things, but not for religious reasons of any kind that I can remember.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well there was a youngest brother of my father who lived close by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to go and visit there because I liked his wife very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was-- she was fun, and they didn't have no children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I used to go and visit her, and she used to bake cookies, cookies for me, like if I didn't have enough at home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there is one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was a very good mother, as I said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the grade one, we had a vaccination-- you know smallpox vaccination-- in school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had a pediatrician, of course, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother send a note to the principal and the teacher in the school that she does not want me to be vaccinated for smallpox at school, that I will be vaccinated privately at our pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then she was waiting for me at school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is grade one, and I remember it like today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were late coming out of class and apparently-- that's what I heard and remember, funnily enough.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mothers were waiting outside for the children, and they said, well, you know, they aren't coming out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of the mothers said, oh yes, they are vaccinating them for smallpox today, so they'll be out a little later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my-- all I remember is the door opening in the classroom and my mother coming in like a lioness.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was just having the-- you know how they do the-- it's not even the injection.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a scratch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was just having it done, and she came.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
